Package: pvflux
Title: Solar PV Power Forecasting with Multiple Transposition and Cell Temperature Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("StÃ©fan", "Janse van Rensburg", , "stefanj@mandela.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0749-2277"))
Description: Implements a modular solar PV power forecasting pipeline with multiple transposition models (Hay-Davies, Olmo), cell temperature models (Skoplaki, Faiman), PVWatts DC output, and simple AC inverter clipping. Supports independent model selection and ensemble analysis. Defaults based on Trina TSM-PC05 module and De Aar site. Incorporates solar position calculation functions from the insol package by Javier G. Corripio.
